        "order": 3,
        "text": "In a bowl, combine ricotta, cooked spinach mixture, egg, half the parmesan, salt, pepper, and nutmeg. Mix well."
      },
      {
        "order": 4,
        "text": "Fill each cannelloni tube with the ricotta-spinach mixture using a spoon or piping bag."
      },
      {
        "order": 5,
        "text": "Spread half the tomato passata evenly in a baking dish. Arrange filled cannelloni over the sauce."
      },
      {
        "order": 6,
        "text": "Pour remaining tomato passata over the cannelloni."
      },
      {
        "order": 7,
        "text": "Make béchamel sauce: melt butter in a saucepan over medium heat, whisk in flour and cook for 1-2 minutes without browning."
      },
      {
        "order": 8,
        "text": "Gradually whisk in milk, continue stirring until sauce thickens and coats the back of a spoon. Season with salt and pepper."
      },
      {
        "order": 9,
        "text": "Pour béchamel evenly over the cannelloni and tomato sauce."
      },
      {
        "order": 10,
        "text": "Sprinkle remaining parmesan on top."
      },
      {
